{"tid":1075772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自從大肚王國覆亡之後，台灣就一直衰到而家","createTime":"2019-03-24T11:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T15:15:08.000Z","uid":225098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1739ffca9cff831206815f1f13d0c66f663a53e","tid":1075772,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6475bdb29eb29512c9c300e40e2db87e3028e01","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來台灣係中國固有領土<br />\n但中原政權從來未曾正式統治"},{"pid":"af2888cbf76b0ab12ea2887169aec0a457c3e2c1","tid":1075772,"uid":225098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6475bdb29eb29512c9c300e40e2db87e3028e01","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來台灣係中國固有領土<br />\n但中原政權從來未曾正式統治"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"中華民國1945至1949年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631a151cf769f69163e6914a96e7fec8c3d545f1","tid":1075772,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"自從大漢帝國覆亡之後，香港就一直衰到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeb816ffba80aa13c3e491388a2fbd3b91a2fde","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2888cbf76b0ab12ea2887169aec0a457c3e2c1","tid":1075772,"uid":225098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6475bdb29eb29512c9c300e40e2db87e3028e01","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來台灣係中國固有領土<br />\n但中原政權從來未曾正式統治"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"中華民國1945至1949年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"1945 年 8 月 15 日，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國杜魯門總統對盟軍最高統帥麥克阿瑟下達第一號總命令，其中規定「在中國（滿州除外）、台灣及北緯十六度以北的法屬印度支那境內之日本將領及所有陸、海、空及附屬部隊應向蔣介石元帥投降」</span>。麥克阿瑟將軍據此發佈一般命令第一號，命中國戰區統帥蔣介石遵令接收。蔣奉命後於 8 月 26 日任命陳儀來台灣實行佔領、接收與受降的任務，開始台灣的軍事佔領。 <span style=\"color: red;\">1949 年 1 月蔣介石在致「台灣省主席兼警備總司令」陳誠的電文清楚表明：「台灣在對日和約未成立前，不過為我國一托管地帶性質，何能明言為剿共最後之堡壘與民族復興之基地」，所以台灣並非「光復」，而是在國際法定義下的「軍事佔領」。</span><br />\n<br />\n只係受命代盟軍接收台灣 越南等地"},{"pid":"1215fc59f4abf91581510690f599aa3a0694318a","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/臺灣光復#/media/File%3A1945_日本在臺北市公會堂向二戰同盟國投降_October_25th%2C_Japan_Surrenders_to_Allies_of_World_War_II_in_Taipei%2C_TAIWAN_(Formosa).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%253A1945_%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%BA%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%82%E5%90%91%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D_October_25th%252C_Japan_Surrenders_to_Allies_of_World_War_II_in_Taipei%252C_TAIWAN_%28Formosa%29.jpg&h=6dc807ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年10月25日，依照盟軍最高統帥麥克阿瑟發佈的《一般命令第一號》[a]，中華民國將領代表同盟國接受在臺日軍投降。<span style=\"color: red;\">臺北公會堂受降典禮台上掛有同盟國英、中、美、蘇四國同等大小的國旗，以及聯合國旗</span>（四國國旗的前面上端，未呈現於畫面）[1]。"},{"pid":"01039bddb31b884c360352fbae568f2d11b94c92","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1215fc59f4abf91581510690f599aa3a0694318a","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/臺灣光復#/media/File%3A1945_日本在臺北市公會堂向二戰同盟國投降_October_25th%2C_Japan_Surrenders_to_Allies_of_World_War_II_in_Taipei%2C_TAIWAN_(Formosa).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%253A1945_%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%BA%E5%8C%97%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%82%E5%90%91%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D_October_25th%252C_Japan_Surrenders_to_Allies_of_World_War_II_in_Taipei%252C_TAIWAN_%28Formosa%29.jpg&h=6dc807ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年10月25日，依照盟軍最高統帥麥克阿瑟發佈的《一般命令第一號》[a]，中華民國將領代表同盟國接受在臺日軍投降。<span style=\"color: red;\">臺北公會堂受降典禮台上掛有同盟國英、中、美、蘇四國同等大小的國旗，以及聯合國旗</span>（四國國旗的前面上端，未呈現於畫面）[1]。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.3kirikou.org/administrator/upload/day_140626/201406261640164416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3kirikou.org%2Fadministrator%2Fupload%2Fday_140626%2F201406261640164416.jpg&h=ffbfdbb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1ebdbb896e25478c05116c7c91abadd21ffe822","tid":1075772,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6475bdb29eb29512c9c300e40e2db87e3028e01","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來台灣係中國固有領土<br />\n但中原政權從來未曾正式統治"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"統治同法理上領土係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f72f47b201d4a228ca62675ee0123be787ef2e5","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ebdbb896e25478c05116c7c91abadd21ffe822","tid":1075772,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6475bdb29eb29512c9c300e40e2db87e3028e01","tid":1075772,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"自古以來台灣係中國固有領土<br />\n但中原政權從來未曾正式統治"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"統治同法理上領土係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"根據何法理？"},{"pid":"2ac0cda1a8b9c604dc7b3ffb5ec42ffb0fdc74ec","tid":1075772,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f72f47b201d4a228ca62675ee0123be787ef2e5","tid":1075772,"uid":35